description:
My place is close to Battery Park 
NY Stock Exchange
Wall Street. You’ll love my place because of the ambiance, the neighborhood, the comfy bed, the outdoors space, and the light. My place is good for couples, solo adventurers, and business travelers.
name: Luxury Apartment on Wall Street.
review: I didn't even get to check in. Host did not leave keys behind and was unavailable to all attempts to contact him. Had to get a hotel room at the last minute.
